title: Scrapheap Challenge - 01x05 - Powerboats.avi
description:
This weeks' Yellow team consists of Major Dick Strawbridge, Kali Monroe, Dave Price and guest specialist Lawrence Newing. 

The Orange team consists of Anne Saunders, Richard 'Bowser' Munson, Shen Chiu and guest specialist Richard Yemm.

The challenge : build a power boat for one and rescue the other team members.

(The video appears 'jittery' for unknown reasons, apologies).

Help me seed (to a ratio of at least 1.5) & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. 

The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them. 

It's a team effort. So please, do your part.
